:<font size="15">בּית לחם</font></div>

===Pronunciation===
בּית לחם / bêyth lechem / bayth leh'-khem

===Etymology===
From [[בּית]] {{HH|1004}} and [[לחם]] {{HH|3899}}; house of bread; 

===Proper noun===
'''בּית לחם'''

# Beth-Lechem, a place in Palestine: - [[Bethlehem]].

